<topic template="Default" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>3.3 Abnormal Spindle Rotation Speed or Start / Stop Timing</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">Abnormal Spindle Rotation Speed or Start / Stop Timing</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="2" style="border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; border-collapse:collapse; cell-border-width:1px; border-color:#000000; border-style:solid;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
        <td style="width:30%; height:27px; background-color:#dddddd;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><text style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold;">Possible Causes</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:70%; height:27px; background-color:#dddddd;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><text style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold;">Corrective Measures</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
        <td style="width:30%; height:22px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:3px; margin-right:3px; margin-bottom:3px; margin-left:3px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">Bearings inside Spindle are damaged</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:70%; height:22px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:3px; margin-right:3px; margin-bottom:3px; margin-left:3px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">Rotate the Spindle nose by hand while it is stopped, and check whether it rotates easily and smoothly, or not.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-right:3px; margin-bottom:3px; margin-left:3px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">If the Spindle does not rotate, or it is hard to rotate, or feels like it is catching on something when it is rotated, the Spindle bearings may be damaged.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-right:3px; margin-bottom:3px; margin-left:3px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">The Spindle bearing needs to be replaced. Contact your Makino service representative.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
</topic>
